{"word":"G5551 - χρονοτριβέω - chronotribéō - khron-ot-rib-eh'-o - Spend time","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χρονοτριβέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">chronotribéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">khron-ot-rib-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Spend time</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - காலம் போக்கு"},{"paragraph":"to wear away time, spend time"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a presumed compound of <a href=\"#/G5550 - χρόνος - chrónos - khron'-os/5550\">G5550</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G5147 - τρίβος - tríbos - tree'-bos/5147\">G5147</a>; to be a <i>time wearer</i>, that is, to <i>procrastinate</i> (<i>linger</i>): - spend time.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5549/5549\">G5549</a>, <a href=\"#/G5550/5550\">G5550</a>, <a href=\"#/G5551/5551\">G5551</a>"}]}